Dialogue: 2,0:03:37.67,0:03:38.63,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}算了 看起来都一样
Dialogue: 2,0:03:38.79,0:03:39.51,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不过我喜欢这个
Dialogue: 2,0:03:40.27,0:03:41.19,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有什么新鲜的
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.19,0:03:42.87,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}iPhone小部件 禁用
Dialogue: 2,0:03:42.87,0:03:45.99,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我们矩形化并尝试默认的窗口吸附
