Dialogue: 2,0:05:25.08,0:05:27.66,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但这个反过来的还不错
Dialogue: 2,0:05:27.66,0:05:28.30,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我喜欢
